Well, the cook - the cook - it was a range in the house, in the living room there was a - an oven you know and a side - pan for water and a range in the middle. That's the only cooking they had 
except in the kitchen. They had a gas ring. A gas - just one ring with a tube attached to a bracket you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 So she did her cooking in the kitchen and took it through to the living room?
