unday dinners and things like that she did it in the living room in the oven you know and - all that - and baking of course. She baked every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 And she did that in the living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did that in the oven, yes. There was no means of cooking in t
he kitchen excepting this ring and - our - I should have said really she was more preparing the meals in the kitchen but she was forced to cook them in the - in the living room 'cos that where the -
