\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 No. They'd have - we'd have - I think we'd have had ours 
