 to make enough at one day, anyway, every day, even when she was working, they made enough dinner at Sunday that there was sufficient just to warm up at Monday. And that was Monday and then Tuesday I think we got to the butchers or something or she made -
 currant puddings or anything what they boil 'em in a cloth, do you know what I mean, we used to have thing like that with some sort of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3302408\charrsid13178822 sauce}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
