\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 And he was caretaker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Football club. Changing room, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did he ever take part in any other sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 No, I don't think - well I can remember earlier, I think he did the cricket club. I can remember having to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 You don't remember him actually participating in any kind of sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 No, I'm not playing - no, I never know him playing, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Your mother's brother used to come up to coincide with the Doncaster races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 From London. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did your father ever go with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 I don't think me father ever went, no, me other uncles did, his brothers. His own brothers, they used to go, yes, but - me father 
didn't go, no. I don't think they did, you see it was during the week isn't it, I don't think they did - perhaps not be able to afford a day off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Would he ever bet on a horse or anything?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 I daresay he did in a light - you know, in a general way
, I think they call in at dinner times but - I never knew much about it. I daresay he would, yes, I daresay he would do but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs, such as a boot or a sick or a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Oh yes, Oddfellowes.
 Yes, he was - he was regular - they were regular attenders at Oddfellowes. It was a sick club wasn't it. They used to have to pay - pay so much - they went every month or something, you see me mother used to say, it's sick club night. And a }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8079967\charrsid13178822 friend}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822  used to
 come up and Keighley that was in as well and they used to go pay it at Mechanics. I can remember as a boy seeing them walk - having a procession with - sort of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8079967\charrsid13178822 regalia}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822  on. And having a ban - a banner yes. Yes. And then when - when the - health came in of 
Lloyd George, you know, you sort of - I was - you had to be in one of these hadn't you. I can remember I was in Oddfellowes, you'd to be associated with a - sick club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 You were compelled to were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 You'd to have - you know, somehow you had to 
be in it I think so, they were in - you could - you could choose which you wanted. I was in Oddfellowes 'cos me father was. And their agent, if you was ill or anything, you went to him for your payment sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did they pay your doctor's bills as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Probably used to do yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Would the Oddfellowes pay your doctor's bills?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 
The Oddfellowes. Probably they would me father but me mother, I don't think it applied to me mother because she had a - she all - she always had a lot of docto
r bills. And they used to because I know - they used to mount up because there used to be a man come round every Friday, doctor's collecting bill. Yes. I suppose that be for us all you know but - 'cos everything was to pay for wasn't it, for the doctor.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 How did you get on with your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 
Oh - me brother? Ever so well, yes. We squabbled and it in the usual way you know but - we always got on well right up to - him dying you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did you feel very close to him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Yes. Yes, I did, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 As a child who would you play with mostly, your brother or your neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Oh I'd a lot of school - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8079967\charrsid13178822 school friends}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid818746\charrsid13178822  you know. Neighbours, lived about and went to same class at school and things like that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did you play out with your brother as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 
Oh well we tended to be in a different group you know, was in different classes, as we got older you know, I went with my friends and he had his you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Where would you play when you were at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Used to play in the stree
ts you know, out of - in the winter nights, we used - at the top of Providence, top of Mill Lane used to be a bright lamp, mostly they were just gas lamps, ordinary naked - naked gas. But at the top of Mill Lane and there was one at top of Providence ther
e, there had an incandescent mantel and send a glorious light, well we used to play under that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 You were saying that the vicar had arranged a special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Yes. Some - somebody - somebody told him that we were gust using at as a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8079967\charrsid13178822 
get-together}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822  you know just for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 To meet your girlfriends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Yes, that's right. And - it lasted a while and it discontinued, I suppose we started joining up and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Where else would you go besides church with this group of friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Oh walking round the countryside mostly and dancing on Saturdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Where would you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 
Oh used to go - in Cross Roads, Howarth. Used to have them in the schools you know, Cross Road School and Howarth school and Keighley occasionally, not often. And - and the Mechani
cs, Oakworth Holding Hall. 'Cos they discontinued all entertainments at the - church. They used - we used to have dances and that there before that during the war time.
