\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822  houses. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Would you have tea at each others houses or would it just be a cup of tea?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Well - a friend would but not - not the group of us you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Just the special friend would?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 The boyfriend would come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Did they expect to know where you were when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 
They were that, yes, I think so. And she liked - even to - up to - even up to getting married she would expect us to be in at ten o'clock on Sat - on Sunday. Yes. She didn't - 
she wasn't tyrannical, she liked to know where we were and what time we were coming in but - you know, we could stay out 'til eleven at Saturday. Sunday she liked us to be in by ten o'clock. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 You were saying that the children played at night where the very bright light was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 So did you play mainly in the street at that time?
