ncy or not I don't know but it was - they put it down that - the baby - it was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13459625\charrsid13178822 weakling}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 .
