\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 No. No, he was a nice - gentle - child, you know, seemed so to me
 and - I think - I generally seemed to know instinctively you know at my age, that he was to he looked after. And he used to - he didn't walk but he - he'd go a great speed you know on his - crawl - crawling along.
