\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid738450 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 What about when you got home in the evenings, who looked after you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167447 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822 Oh well of course - we - we came home at midday, we all met - met at midday and had our di
nner together and then we came home - we - now where was the key - they left a key somewhere for us to get in from school about four o'clock, and they came home about half past five. Well I'd just to see that the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13459625\charrsid13178822 kettle}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid818746\charrsid13178822  was boiling for half past five and - then nothing - you know, nobody else looked after us. No. No.
